      • getPayloadKeys

        java.util.Set<java.lang.String> getPayloadKeys()
        Retrieves the action payload keys. If this is an predefined SDK, the payload will contain the action value key.
        Returns:
        The action payload keys.

      • getPayloadValue

        java.lang.String getPayloadValue(java.lang.String key)
        This method retrieves an action payload value by a given key
        Parameters:
        key - The payload value key
        Returns:
        The payload key's value. If this is an predefined SDK, the result for action value key will be as follows:
        typevalue
        urlThe url that will be opened
        dialThe phone number that will be dialed
        customThe notification name of the intent that will be started
